find below samples of lua rule expressions for creating rules.
the function clause must be placed in the expression field when creating an expression for a rule.

### expired card expression

function main(iso_transaction)
if iso_transaction[39] == "33" then
return true
else
return false
end
end


### reconcile error  expression

function main(iso_transaction)
if iso_transaction[39] == "95" then
return true
else
return false
end
end


### succesful transaction expression
function main(iso_transaction)
if iso_transaction[39] == "00" then
return true
else
return false
end
end


### balance enquiry  expression
function main(iso_transaction)
if iso_transaction[3] == "310000" then
return true
else
return false
end
end

